title._content: Faulkner, Charles S. of Keene NH

description._content: TITLE Faulkner, Charles S. of Keene NH CREATOR SUBJECT Men - NH - Keene Business people, American - NH - Keene DESCRIPTION Photograph of Charles Stearns Faulkner of Keene New Hampshire. Charles was born in 1819 in Keene and died in 1879. He went into his father's clothier mills business at age 23 and in 1846 went into another family business, the Cheshire Steam Mills. He married Sallie Elyn Eames and had 6 children.
